    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297080/extras/ef3c039824b57ee727ee701d4b1f5d15.avif?t=1764298231\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297080/extras_big/ef3c039824b57ee727ee701d4b1f5d15.avif?t=1764298231 width=800 height=153 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 你的姥姥给你留下了一份惊喜大礼——一个位于神秘山谷的度假村山庄，蓝楹山庄！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 这座山庄位于一个以女性为主要居住人群的西南山谷，是一个颇具少数民族风情的世外桃源。但这里除了有你熟悉的家乡气息，似乎还隐藏着一些不为人知的秘密，而这些秘密都与你小时候从姥姥处听闻的失落神话有关……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 虽然当务之急似乎是好好利用这里神奇的种植技术、神秘的当地科技来重振山庄的辉煌！但……有趣的事情这么多，尽管自由定义你的经营目标，去探索这奇幻未知的沐月山谷，和姐姐们共同尝试有关蓝楹山庄的一切可能性吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 至于姥姥去哪了？别担心，她只是来了一场说走就走的旅行，骑上机车出发了而已！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297080/extras/d9412d5367bcaf2b36e040c10ee25d51.avif?t=1764298231\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297080/extras_big/d9412d5367bcaf2b36e040c10ee25d51.avif?t=1764298231 width=800 height=74 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297080/extras/60d47b58d0e73fb2db275d828a1d02cb.webp?t=1764298231\" width=17 height=24 /></span>西南特色作物+花式嫁接！炼金术般的奇妙体验让你根本停不下来~</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297080/extras/d0dd128be7a6a24d119b529133188910.webp?t=1764298231\" width=18 height=15 /></span>饲养你的小动物朋友们~当然还有必不可少的钓鱼！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297080/extras/1e2de762c5e51124693d7c4641873cfe.webp?t=1764298231\" width=19 height=24 /></span>自由度超高的烹饪！多种食材和烹饪方式任你挑选~用高超的厨艺来让餐厅声名远扬吧！（但如果失败了的话……嘿嘿）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297080/extras/72e0b6d0d761e8418631617d72c14b57.poster.avif?t=1764298231\" width=800 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297080/extras/72e0b6d0d761e8418631617d72c14b57.webm?t=1764298231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297080/extras/3588fe0441358f9612dc56347ddf3070.webp?t=1764298231\" width=19 height=24 /></span>用各式各样的家具来打造属于你的山庄，吸引更多的游客吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297080/extras/df5de756c5922072fb473d871bbb5133.avif?t=1764298231\" width=300 height=282 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297080/extras/a1748234aab35a619f291afcd213bfde.avif?t=1764298231\" width=300 height=282 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297080/extras/98ef5709a2925d140d532b789502dc3f.webp?t=1764298231\" width=28 height=32 /></span>经营你的纪念品商店！用探险中发现的灵感来设计独一无二的山庄特色产品吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297080/extras/f4c80001468f1dd0f375c776185b1cc4.webp?t=1764298231\" width=24 height=20 /></span>事情太多了忙不过来？别担心！作为BOSS你还可以进行直聘！招募更多员工来帮忙壮大山庄吧！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297080/extras/5437cb1bd53f084dd0a4f5089106f4e0.avif?t=1764298231\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297080/extras_big/5437cb1bd53f084dd0a4f5089106f4e0.avif?t=1764298231 width=800 height=61 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297080/extras/1391fea7aa8c8fcca0357265d36fc06d.webp?t=1764298231\" width=15 height=13 /></span>和你的朋友们见面聊天、了解她们的过去，与她们一起去找点乐子，发展深刻的情谊吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297080/extras/79ef162189342ac6de0aaafdaf81af90.poster.avif?t=1764298231\" width=800 height=284 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297080/extras/79ef162189342ac6de0aaafdaf81af90.webm?t=1764298231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297080/extras/806a183bff89ce56cb7b214e56db28f1.webp?t=1764298231\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297080/extras/806a183bff89ce56cb7b214e56db28f1.poster.avif?t=1764298231\" class=\"bb_img\" width=31 height=18 /></picture></span>当个快乐的该溜子！在小镇与山间闲逛，说不定还能听到有趣的八卦！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297080/extras/59d73c4643d4e71199c1b4d643aa4c34.webp?t=1764298231\" width=24 height=24 /></span>进行野外探索！探索山野传闻、精怪传说背后的秘密！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297080/extras/417cf816b845ca5ab1c352b37aaa7118.poster.avif?t=1764298231\" width=800 height=412 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297080/extras/417cf816b845ca5ab1c352b37aaa7118.webm?t=1764298231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297080/extras/417cf816b845ca5ab1c352b37aaa7118.mp4?t=1764298231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
